Iris
====
Visual exploration of omics data



INSTALLATION
------------
TODO: Make installation a lot more streamlined....

# Fetch external modules
$ git submodule init
$ git submodule update

# Install FastBit
$ cd fastbit
$ ./configure --prefix ../
$ make
# Take a [long] coffee break
$ make check
$ make install

# Install Node.js dependencies
$ cd ../nodejs
$ npm install

RUNNING IRIS
------------
$ cd nodejs
$ node app.js

